AGR5.
FY 2027 Base Plans:
FY 2027 M-Code planned activities include completion of EMD. EMD efforts include Proof of Manufacturing
hardware and final software qualification, and achieve Security Approval of an M-Code capable Tactical
Tomahawk (TACTOM) AGR5.
