Homing (ARH) seeker and Millimeter Wave (MMW) terminal seeker capabilities against threat systems to
evaluate lethality improvement options. FMA assessments will remain focused on emerging modern complex
threat systems as well as theater/country-specific systems of interest. Expect continued testing and evaluation
on advanced Surface-to-Air weapons and related IADS, jammers, and ARM countermeasures.




