D. Acquisition Strategy
ARM system updates are provided through the System Support Activity (SSA) at Naval Air Warfare Center - Weapons Division (NAWCWD), China Lake, CA. ARM fleet
priorities are set by the Fleet ARM Steering Committee. FMA procurement of surrogate threat system hardware components are executed through supplier contracts and
deliver to the Government team for integration into complete surrogate threat systems. Hardware components expense upon the delivery of end items, which normally
take 12 months to deliver.


