systems, electro-optical/infrared (EO/IR) sensors, sophisticated data processing algorithms, and integrated data
fusion and processing systems. By demonstrating these technologies in a relevant operational environment,
this program will prove their effectiveness and readiness for integration into a broader system of systems. This
integrated system will provide airfield managers and operational commanders with a comprehensive, real-time
picture of FOD hazards, allowing for proactive and risk-based mitigation strategies.
