- Continue development of predictive and prognostic analytic models that use artificial intelligence and machine
learning (AI/ML) to provide outputs to Marine Maintainers enabling action before failure.
- Continue development of tools to integrate analytic model outputs with system of record and supply support
entities to overcome supply chain challenges.
-Initiate the assessment of the CBM+ hardware integration with tactical networks and data loggers onto the ACV
platform, including all technical, environmental, and cybersecurity requirements.
-Initiate the conduction of environmental testing, including saltwater immersion, and develop platform-specific
installation kits (mounts, cables, and brackets) to integrate data loggers.
